  <h2>Professional Summary</h2>
  <p>
    Creative and multidisciplinary Freelance Artist with over 25 years of experience in visual arts, design strategy, and art education. Founder and Creative Director of Studio Kalavritt, a Pune-based design studio specializing in bespoke illustration, mural design, and visual storytelling. Currently serving as an Assistant Professor of Design, blending academic rigor with practical insights. Proven expertise in mentoring young designers, leading community art projects, and curating exhibitions across India.
  </p>

